```{r}
MI <- read.csv("data/Myocardial infarction complications Database.csv")
MI <- MI[,c(2:112, 121)]
dim(MI)

NApercent <- colSums(is.na(MI)) / nrow(MI)
selectcol <- NApercent[NApercent < 0.1]
MI.work <- MI[, names(selectcol)]
MI.work <- na.omit(MI.work)
dim(MI.work)
```
